        <div class="lawCont">
        	<h1>女儿成绩很好，高考却选择艺考，我为什么支持她？——来自一位妈妈的自述</h1>
            <div class="lawContInfo">
            	<span>来源：王者</span>
                <span>发表时间：2019-10-29 10:00:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="lawContDiv">
                <section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">说是“那年”，其实就是去年，可能是想把那段经历埋藏在记忆深处吧！<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">高考对每一个考生和家庭都是一场没有硝烟的战争。对于我们这个基本上没有把学习成绩作为首要评判标准的家庭来说，并没有意识到战争的来临。但是由于女儿选择了一条更加艰难的高考路，使得我们这场战争异常惨烈。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">01</span></strong></span></p></section><p><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 105, 172); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">关于抉择</strong></span></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">学习成绩那么好，怎么学艺术呢？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">这是所有知道我们选择的亲戚朋友包括女儿老师的疑问。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在他们看来，参加艺考的都是学习成绩低的孩子的无奈选择。</strong>因为艺考的文化课成绩要求不高，成绩这么好岂不是浪费了？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我就举了这样一个简单的例子。比如说，我有十元钱，可以买到一块儿精美的蛋糕，但是我宁愿只花两元钱买个面包。原因是虽然蛋糕比面包贵且我也买得起，但是我喜欢面包。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我不会为了让别人看到我有财力买得起蛋糕而去选择蛋糕。</strong>比喻可能简单粗糙些，但实质差不多。朋友们见我如此说，虽嘴上不反驳什么，其实内心仍无法理解。好吧！<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们的决定不是要别人理解，不能活在别人的眼睛里。</strong></span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 105, 172); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">女儿从小就喜欢涂鸦，我们家长对绘画都是门外汉，既无鉴赏力亦无法指导，只是任由其画。她的书架上满满的各种漫画书，对漫画、动画都喜欢得不得了。这应该也是大多数孩子的表现吧！但是更多的孩子随着学业的负担加重，一点点放弃或消磨了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">女儿却没有受到任何限制，照样逛书店买漫画书，随时都可以画上几笔。假期还带她参加各种漫展。成为漫画家便成了她的梦想。初中毕业时，自已便有了明确的目标。然而，真正到了需要最后抉择时，并没有像选蛋糕或面包那样简单，还是经历了一番挣扎。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.6666667" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWkdZCeGLr77TfO4GBycsfD8So7Xic1nQJjFXmOiccOgYWpAUXJ0rj78tQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" _width="677px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWkdZCeGLr77TfO4GBycsfD8So7Xic1nQJjFXmOiccOgYWpAUXJ0rj78tQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">高二的暑期，最后抉择的时刻来临了。如果决定高考报考动画专业，此时就要离开学校，去北京参加专业课的集训了。从集训到专业课考试结束要七、八个月，这期间文化课就完全搁置了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">这样就存在一个很大的风险。就是一旦专业课考试不合格，不仅不能报考动画专业，而且原本还不错的文化课成绩肯定也会大跳水，选择别的好一点的学校也不可能了。<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">懂事的女儿对于集训期间要支付比较高的各项费用，也是内心颇有负担的。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在反复的纠结中，甚至还有了如果付出这么大代价考上了，将来不喜欢了呢的担心。怎么办？走在人生的十字路口，这也是女儿人生的第一个重要的路口。如何抉择？决定当然要她自已做（<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从小到大，凡是涉及她自已的事，只要符合她年龄的决定，都要她自已拿主意</strong>）。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">其实，我的内心也是矛盾的。凭着文化课成绩，女儿基本上是可以稳稳当当地选择个还不错的重点大学，而且她对哲学、心理学也是很有兴趣的。如果选择艺考，就增加了不确定性，就可能会面临“损了夫人又折兵”的境地。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">大多数的父母都会希望自己的孩子安安稳稳，而不是一波三折或是披荆斩棘。我也不例外。但我了解我的孩子，如果不选择动画，这会成为她一生的遗憾。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">失败可以重来，但遗憾可能终将无法弥补。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我告诉她，面临选择可以做减法，不要让更多的外在的因素干扰自已的判断，要回归内心，倾听自己内心的声音。做个漫画家一直是你的梦想。不管将来你是否还喜欢，至少当下你喜欢。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有梦想就要努力去实现它。</strong>不要怕失败，你还年轻，有时间去尝试适合自已的路。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">如果，你屈从于现实，选择了比较容易获得且在别人看来很光鲜而你自已却并不很喜欢的“蛋糕”，那么“面包”永远是你的遗憾。遗憾是一种痛。人生是一次单程旅行，尽可能不要留下遗憾的痛。钱，爸爸妈妈可以赚，我们努力这么多年，就是为了助力你实现梦想。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">最终，女儿踏上了参加集训的路。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.667" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWBN32cZwZYM33JianDd1ZOZo8gfNNuXnJicsyj4mpkL4NRx4vp7833HZQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1000" _width="677px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWBN32cZwZYM33JianDd1ZOZo8gfNNuXnJicsyj4mpkL4NRx4vp7833HZQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">02</span></strong></span></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; color: rgb(96, 105, 172);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">艺考绝不是通向大学的捷径</strong></span></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">家有艺考生，才真正感受到了艺考的惨烈，更加颠覆了艺考是通向大学捷径的绝对错误的观念。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我的孩子凭着喜爱和一腔热血，一头扎进了动画专业考前集训班。虽然一直喜欢画，但都是盲目的随意的画，没有受过任何专业的训练，无论是针对绘画基础，还是动画专业，女儿都是零。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">而参加集训的同学，一些是美院附中的，一些是有绘画家庭环境的，还有一些是在其他培训机构受过专业训练的，像女儿这样零基础的极少。之前虽然对集训的困难有心理准备，但却是大大低估了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">与坐在课堂上学文化课不同，集训的课程更多的是动手画，老师讲的相对少。集训的前几个月，女儿基本处在不会画，听不懂，画不完……各种懵、晕的状态。加之有生以来第一次这么长时间离开家，饮食起居都要自己操心。陌生人，陌生环境，各种不适应。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">压力一下子如巨石般砸过来，生理及心理都几近崩溃。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">远在千里之外的我更是急得不得了。但隔行如隔山呀！我无法给出任何有针对性的引导，况且又不在身边无法面对面的沟通。我意识到了女儿所面临的情况有多糟。首先是对专业课学习的难度估计不足；其次一部分压力来源与身边同学的比较；还有就是各种担心顾虑---考不过多丢人呀！文化课落了这么长时间还能跟上吗？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">与同龄孩子比，女儿虽然相对自立坚强。但她毕竟还是个孩子，面临这么大的压力还是头一回，她能扛过来吗？每天女儿在北京的集训班上焦头烂额，我在家里如热锅上的蚂蚁，心神不宁，坐卧不安。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">但我强迫自己一定要稳住，一定不能把急躁的情绪传递给女儿。只有我先稳下来，她才有可能稳下来。我虽不能给孩子专业性的引导，但我可以帮她缓解压力和紧张情绪。我坚信兴趣是最好的老师。我坚信女儿这种情况是暂时的。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">自己内心笃定，才能把沉稳的情绪传递给她。</strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 105, 172); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>虽然她的时间极为宝贵，每天都有画不完的作业，但我们还是每天要有半小时到一小时的电话沟通。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.6731481" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mW2Wc1AAAWLu8icmTJc1ibVNe9SkG0mTQWIfsyJ5LQA85ef9tJibSNZN09A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" _width="677px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mW2Wc1AAAWLu8icmTJc1ibVNe9SkG0mTQWIfsyJ5LQA85ef9tJibSNZN09A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我告诉她从学文化课到学专业课，这也算是跨界了，教、学的方法都不同了，不适应是正常的，要有一个过渡过程，千万急不得。而且，每个同学的基础是不同的，暂时不要跟同学比，不能看到同学画得又快又好心里就慌了，尽可能做到心无旁骛。无论画得有多烂，硬着头皮画下去。听不懂要多问老师，多跟画得好的同学交流。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">而且，我交了底给她。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们努力了，考不过也无所谓，为梦想我们尝试了，没有什么可丢人的。</strong>况且这个过程也是难得的人生历练，单凭这一点，就没有白努力。这些不仅仅是劝慰她的话，我内心也的确是做好了这样的准备。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">在我的建议下，她改变作息时间。每天12点之前必须入睡。早上6点钟起床，6点多就到画室，有时会惹得保洁阿姨很不满。一个人在画室很安静，心也就静，注意力很容易集中。而且，还可以仔细鉴赏悬挂在画室墙上的同学们的优秀作品，从中可以模仿和借鉴。坚持一段时间后，因为熬夜以及压力脖子上起的红疹逐渐褪去，身体状况有所好转，精力也充足了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我们的“话疗”每天都坚持不断。她每天都要告知这一天她画的情况。画得好了，得到老师认可了，会欢天喜地，然后我们全家都会兴奋不已，并给予她更多的鼓励。真心感谢陈亚楠老师，她的一句“孺子可教”给了女儿极大的激励。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">然而，更多的时候是因画不好而情绪低落，此时，我尽可能的使出浑身解数安慰我的孩子。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我尽可能的让我安慰的语言具体而妥贴，防止一些大话空话引起她的反感。</strong>我的安慰可能起不到作用，但是至少我可以做个不良情绪的垃圾桶，她把一天的郁闷不快纠结都宣泄出来，也会起到一定的减压效果。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">由于我日常工作也是忙得不可开交，而且每天面对的都是各种纠纷和陷于纠纷中的人们，我自身就会沾染了些许负面情绪。所以，在与女儿的沟通中，偶而我也会出现不堪重负的情况，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">对于她的发泄有时也会不耐烦，但基本都能及时意识到而采取补救措施。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">期间，既便是在如此紧张疯狂的集训中，她几乎是每个月回家一次，为了节省时间，往返只能乘飞机，有时只是停留半天时间，但我们觉得这是必要的。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">面对面的交流会更深入透彻，在家里住上一晚也会让我的孩子积蓄更多的力量。</strong>磨刀不误砍柴功吧！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWwpVh3YDJzA46G1TQdvOpBiaoBoX0eoqz1Ye7EZdl6DIY8Nt5fTrgEZA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1000" _width="677px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWwpVh3YDJzA46G1TQdvOpBiaoBoX0eoqz1Ye7EZdl6DIY8Nt5fTrgEZA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">从8月1日至次年的2月末，在这七个月的时间里，我的孩子是拼尽了全力了。最后的结果能怎样，我们谁都不知道。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">过了春节，正月初八，我和孩子爸爸踏上进京的列车。<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们要在接下来的一周（2月24日至3月3日）艺考中，陪伴我的孩子进行最后的战斗。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我一直认为我是个很有承受能力的人。但下车的当天就病了，症状类似中暑，上吐下泄，可时值残冬天气还很冷，怎么可能？孩子爸爸说我是内火攻心。是吗？我一直怀疑这病的突然。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当时怕影响孩子考试，不敢告诉她，硬撑着帮她整理画材，准备考试用具、证件；一起踏查考场，计算几个学校间的乘车距离（女儿报了中国传媒大学、北京电影学院、北京师范大学三所学校的七个专业的校考，考试时间是穿插的），并提前约好车；考察好考场周边的餐饮，选好吃什么更安全可口又省时。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.2px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">前几天的考试我还可以撑着在考场外等着迎接她。但几天的水米不进，已让我没有力气再站起来，我恨自己病得不是时候，生怕影响孩子的情绪。还好我们住的宾馆就在最后的考场附近，孩子爸爸可以兼顾起来。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">终于考完了啦！不管怎样，我们都松了一口气，像是卸下了千斤重担，一下子轻松了。我终于可以把我的孩子带回家啦！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">03</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 105, 172); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">艰难的文化课备考</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2018年3月4日到家，3月5日高三正式开学了。距离高考不足百天，我的孩子没有一点喘息时间就又投入到文化课的复习中。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">女儿的文化课基础原本很好。怎奈，落了七个多月呀！跟同学已无法同步，课堂上也跟不上老师的进度。面对数学、化学卷子上的题目都似曾相识，却找不到解题的方法。就是比较有优势的物理、英语也吃力得很。开学没几天，学校组织第一次模拟考试。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">女儿跟我说不想参加考试。</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">好吧！</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不考就不考，我也害怕不理想的成绩伤害她的自尊心和自信心。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">怎么办？不能等，不能靠了，如果继续跟着学校复习，恐怕三个月后的高考不会有太大进展。专业课的成绩要在4月中旬才发布。期间，我的孩子必须全力以赴复习文化课，因为如果专业课不合格，还要指望着凭借文化课的成绩能有更多的选择。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.592" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWzvQ3Qq7ZG1k9rJ17aYAPOmMV45ic7SaIn488va4CIxgU8C1Ab11LfbA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1000" _width="677px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KsWZkOXh2lrCv9dqsw51Eb3KZERas9mWzvQ3Qq7ZG1k9rJ17aYAPOmMV45ic7SaIn488va4CIxgU8C1Ab11LfbA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section class="" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">女儿从小学到高中，从来没在校外补习过任何科目。现在无法与校内同步，必须寻求校外的渠道了，而且为了高效，只能是一对一的方式。发动亲朋好友，多方打听，选定了数学老师；原来教女儿的物理老师肯帮忙补习，真是感激不尽呀；最好的姐妹的表弟就是高中化学老师中佼佼者，我孩子真是幸运呀！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">然而再高明的老师也不可能让孩子成绩立竿见影。密集的模拟考试来临了，女儿的成绩比集训前下降了一百分左右。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">巨大的压力再次袭来，好在这一次我们在一起，共同面对。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">她每天要学到很晚，有时甚至到凌晨。从小到大，我们没有伴读的习惯。每天都是我们家长先入睡，至于女儿学到几点，学了什么，我们根本不清楚。我当然以为，我的孩子是在复习功课，并且总是心疼地劝她要早睡。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">一天，她爸爸送她上学走后，整理她的房间，发现她的手机在床上。难到睡觉前还用手机吗？我从来没有偷窥过女儿的隐私，但这是高考的节骨眼儿上呀，我不得不违反我的一贯原则，翻看了她的手机。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">这一看不要紧，我简直懵掉了。我的孩子在追星！怎么可能？女儿向来对各种追星族嗤之以鼻，认为是些无脑的人才会如此。如今她自已却……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">距离高考不            </div>
